All these things are already pre-planned.

00:00:35.644 --> 00:00:43.183
That He should be born in a manger
in difficult situations,

00:00:44.208 --> 00:00:48.591
to show that whether you are born
poor or rich,

00:00:48.792 --> 00:00:55.965
whether you are born in difficulties
or in problems,

00:00:56.166 --> 00:01:01.607
if you have Divinity within you it shines
by itself.

00:01:05.844 --> 00:01:17.657
As the Christianity took a very wrong
deviated line,

00:01:18.808 --> 00:01:24.878
they have never been able to understand
the significance of Christ.

00:01:25.085 --> 00:01:35.053
To them Immaculate Conception is absolutely
not possible.

00:01:35.254 --> 00:01:40.657
Most of the people think that it's some
sort of a mythical story.

00:01:42.366 --> 00:01:46.869
But in India we do believe

00:01:47.070 --> 00:02:01.949
that Gauri created Shri Ganesha out
of Her own vibrations

00:02:02.150 --> 00:02:07.954
and that He became the Deity of Mooladhara.

00:02:08.155 --> 00:02:12.805
We accept it. But not in the West.

