They will never accept such a thing

00:02:15.170 --> 00:02:22.329
because their mental side is over-developed
and dominates them.

00:02:24.265 --> 00:02:30.747
Maybe they are not so very old like Indians

00:02:30.948 --> 00:02:35.628
to understand that above all is God.

00:02:35.829 --> 00:02:40.545
Even the concept of God is quite mental.

00:02:41.505 --> 00:02:45.438
Moreover, the way Christianity has been,

00:02:45.639 --> 00:02:51.621
it has not provided any proper guidance.

00:02:51.822 --> 00:02:57.834
On the contrary, whenever they have failed
they said: "It's a mystery."

00:02:59.518 --> 00:03:04.459
But it's very simple to understand
for Indians,

00:03:04.660 --> 00:03:08.229
that anything is possible for God.

00:03:08.430 --> 00:03:13.343
After all He is God. He is God Almighty.

00:03:13.544 --> 00:03:21.262
Because of this mental attitude which
is much lower

00:03:21.463 --> 00:03:26.074
than the knowledge of your Spirit,

00:03:26.275 --> 00:03:30.581
the ordinary, mundane type of this
superficial knowledge

00:03:30.782 --> 00:03:39.927
can never allow the personality to accept
the greatness of God.

00:03:42.333 --> 00:03:46.526
I had a grandma. She was My father's aunt

00:03:46.727 --> 00:03:54.435
and she used to tell us a nice story about
somebody who was going to meet God.

00:03:54.636 --> 00:03:58.070
Of course this - in India everybody
understands all these things.

00:03:58.271 --> 00:04:01.271
They will not say: "How is he going to meet
God?" but they accept, you see:

00:04:01.472 --> 00:04:02.852
“All right, he is going to meet God”.

00:04:03.053 --> 00:04:08.065
So when he was going on the way,
on the road, he found one gentleman

00:04:08.266 --> 00:04:14.351
sitting there, nicely singing songs,
bhajans of God,

00:04:14.552 --> 00:04:18.205
doing nothing on the roadside.

00:04:18.406 --> 00:04:21.317
So he said: "Oh, so you are going
to meet God?"

00:04:21.517 --> 00:04:26.476
"Yes, I am going to meet Him. So have
you any message for Him?"

00:04:26.677 --> 00:04:30.447
"Yes, please tell Him that I'm all right,

00:04:30.648 --> 00:04:37.156
but He should arrange for my food, because
I think the food is now finishing."

00:04:37.357 --> 00:04:40.853
He said: "Really, that's what you want
me to tell Him?"

00:04:41.054 --> 00:04:49.246
"Yes, yes, please tell Him. Oh, of course
He'll arrange, but please tell Him."

00:04:49.447 --> 00:04:53.146
So he went ahead and he met another
gentleman

00:04:53.347 --> 00:04:56.437
who was standing on his head, or
in a Christian way I would say

00:04:56.638 --> 00:05:01.422
he was going to church every day with nice
suits, and singing hymns every day,

00:05:01.623 --> 00:05:04.767
listening to the pastor's sermons, or
whatever you may say;

00:05:04.968 --> 00:05:08.540
and in the Indian way we can say he was
going to the temple every day,

00:05:08.741 --> 00:05:13.422
standing on his head, doing all kinds
of yoga asanas and everything.

00:05:13.623 --> 00:05:18.459
And he asked him: "Please go and ask
God - I've tried everything.

00:05:18.660 --> 00:05:21.169
When is He going to meet me? I would
like to see Him.

00:05:21.370 --> 00:05:23.966
I would like to have His darshan."
He said: "All right."

00:05:24.167 --> 00:05:29.779
So he went to God,

00:05:29.980 --> 00:05:35.317
and whatever work he had he finished
with it,

00:05:35.518 --> 00:05:40.221
and then God asked him: "Have you got
anything to tell Me?"

00:05:40.422 --> 00:05:47.393
He said: "Nothing much, but I met one
gentleman while coming

00:05:47.594 --> 00:05:51.429
and he said that 'I'm doing all kinds
of things, I have tried everything,

00:05:51.644 --> 00:05:54.352
and when will God meet me? I am standing
on my head,

00:05:54.553 --> 00:05:58.737
and I am doing also all kinds of yoga
asanas, and all kinds of things,

00:05:58.938 --> 00:06:02.276
and also I am going to church and
mosque, I am praying,

00:06:02.477 --> 00:06:08.197
doing all sorts of prayers, but when will
God meet me?'"

00:06:08.398 --> 00:06:12.172
So God said: "Tell him he has to do little
more.

00:06:12.373 --> 00:06:17.397
See, it's not easy. When Sahaja Yoga
will come we'll see!"

00:06:28.512 --> 00:06:32.604
So then even he said: "And there’s another
one who was on the road, You see.

00:06:32.805 --> 00:06:35.802
He was just enjoying himself singing songs,

00:06:36.003 --> 00:06:37.950
he suddenly saw me, and he told me:

00:06:38.150 --> 00:06:41.128
'You see, my food is now finishing, ask
God to arrange it for me.'"

00:06:41.329 --> 00:06:45.342
He said: "Really, is the food just
finishing?" Immediately God said:

00:06:45.543 --> 00:06:48.889
"What are you doing, why don't you go
and look after him? His food is finishing."

00:06:49.090 --> 00:06:52.208
"No, no, Sir, we yesterday only, we
arranged it, all that."

00:06:52.409 --> 00:06:55.488
He said: "All right, all right, doesn't
matter." You see, he couldn't understand,

00:06:55.689 --> 00:06:57.685
you know, that this fellow who is trying
all these things

00:06:57.886 --> 00:07:00.902
and God is still saying that he has
to wait.

00:07:01.103 --> 00:07:04.559
And while this fellow is just singing songs
of God and all that,

00:07:04.760 --> 00:07:08.874
and why is it so much impressed by this
another fellow

00:07:09.075 --> 00:07:14.312
who is doing nothing to seek God?

00:07:14.725 --> 00:07:17.754
So then God realized that he is in some
sort of an illusion.

00:07:17.955 --> 00:07:22.653
So He told him: "All right, you go and tell
them one thing.

00:07:22.854 --> 00:07:28.335
To both of them the same thing, that 'When
I went to God what I saw there

00:07:28.536 --> 00:07:36.803
was that He made a camel pass through
the eye of a needle.'"

00:07:38.503 --> 00:07:41.689
So he said: "Really, I should tell them?"

00:07:41.890 --> 00:07:44.972
"Yes, yes, you just tell them, and see
the reaction."

00:07:45.173 --> 00:07:49.342
So he went down. So this is, the first one
met him, he said: "What God has said?"

00:07:49.543 --> 00:07:53.250
He said that God has said: "Wait till
Sahaja Yoga comes in, then I'll meet you.

00:07:53.451 --> 00:07:55.872
Before that you go round like this."

00:07:56.073 --> 00:07:58.122
"Oh God, when will this Sahaja Yoga come?"

00:07:58.352 --> 00:08:00.716
And he said: "So, but He'll meet me
sometime?

00:08:00.917 --> 00:08:05.539
I hope Sahaja Yoga also comes some time."

00:08:05.840 --> 00:08:08.489
And he was quite disappointed.

00:08:08.690 --> 00:08:13.221
So he went and he asked him that:
"What did you see with,

00:08:13.422 --> 00:08:16.779
there when you went to see God?"
He said: "I saw that, you know,

00:08:16.980 --> 00:08:20.979
He passed a camel through the eye
of an, of a needle."

00:08:21.193 --> 00:08:25.014
He said: "What? How is it possible?
It's impossible!" -

00:08:25.245 --> 00:08:27.965
Now mental - "How is it possible,

00:08:28.166 --> 00:08:31.131
that a camel can pass through the eye,
it's not possible,

00:08:31.332 --> 00:08:36.586
see the volume of this one and such
a little thing. How can he pass?

00:08:36.787 --> 00:08:39.586
No, no, no, no you are just telling me
a story because you have been to God,

00:08:39.787 --> 00:08:43.814
you are trying to show off, that's all. I,
I don't believe in all this nonsense.

00:08:44.015 --> 00:08:47.511
You see, you are just telling me lies,
and don't try to befool me."

00:08:47.712 --> 00:08:52.325
So he went to another person who was
on the street eating nicely.

00:08:52.526 --> 00:08:55.309
He said: "How are you?" "Oh, I know He had
arranged before you reached there,

00:08:55.510 --> 00:08:59.705
I know it was all right after all. You see,
He looks after me all the time.

00:08:59.906 --> 00:09:05.409
So what did you see when you went there?"
He said: "I saw that God Almighty

00:09:05.610 --> 00:09:12.397
passed a camel through an eye of a
needle. It's a very amazing thing."

00:09:12.598 --> 00:09:17.803
He said: "What amazing thing? He is God,
do you know He is God?

00:09:18.004 --> 00:09:24.888
Do you know He is God? God can do
anything. He can do anything!"

00:09:25.089 --> 00:09:33.448
That's made him understand, that if you
understand that God is all-powerful -

00:09:33.649 --> 00:09:37.842
all-powerful, it doesn't mean that He can
move Himalayas to Maharashtra.

00:09:38.043 --> 00:09:41.160
It doesn't mean that!

00:09:50.536 --> 00:09:54.162
But it means He is all powerful.

00:09:54.363 --> 00:09:58.263
Means He can do subtlest and subtlest
thing, and such things

00:09:58.464 --> 00:10:03.626
which our brain, this mental side cannot
understand.

00:10:03.827 --> 00:10:09.714
It's beyond the conception of a human mind.

00:10:11.653 --> 00:10:15.100
This is what God is.

00:10:15.301 --> 00:10:17.946
He is the One who has created human beings.

00:10:18.147 --> 00:10:20.170
He has to be beyond us if He is creating.

00:10:20.378 --> 00:10:23.626
If a potter creates a pot that means
he is beyond the pot.

00:10:23.827 --> 00:10:27.357
Pot cannot create God... the potter.

00:10:27.558 --> 00:10:33.053
And the potter has created the pot,
so that means that this pot

00:10:33.254 --> 00:10:38.193
which is created by him has to be -
something which is made by him,

00:10:38.394 --> 00:10:43.757
so he has to be much more powerful
than the pot is.

00:10:45.250 --> 00:10:52.877
But it is unbelievable, or say, beyond
the conception of human beings,

00:10:53.078 --> 00:11:02.824
that what a God it must be Who has made
this great computer.

00:11:04.141 --> 00:11:07.395
We take everything for granted.

00:11:07.596 --> 00:11:13.510
We cannot even make a particle of clay
ourself.

00:11:14.359 --> 00:11:17.230
We cannot make anything, human beings
cannot make.

00:11:17.431 --> 00:11:20.454
Ha, if there is some stone, all right, you
can put this up.

00:11:20.655 --> 00:11:25.428
If there is some clay, you can make some
sort of a house out of it.

00:11:25.629 --> 00:11:29.019
But it’s all dead from the dead.

00:11:31.836 --> 00:11:43.312
But can you make a candle which will
burn badhas?

00:11:47.538 --> 00:11:54.782
You have seen it with your own eyes that
before My photograph the badhas burn.

00:11:54.983 --> 00:11:58.049
Can you do that?

00:12:00.620 --> 00:12:07.202
Now you, we have no, also the idea
of the complete, intricate working,

00:12:07.403 --> 00:12:18.695
delicate machinery, and also very dynamic
explosive machinery,

00:12:18.896 --> 00:12:24.370
how it works to create human beings,
to create all this universe,

00:12:24.571 --> 00:12:31.702
to create all these beautiful flowers and
trees and everything.

00:12:31.903 --> 00:12:36.671
Look at the stars. Look at how many
they are.

00:12:36.872 --> 00:12:41.849
Out of that He has chosen this Mother Earth
to create human beings.

00:12:42.050 --> 00:12:45.465
How He has made it?

00:12:47.627 --> 00:12:56.636
When He wants to send His own Son, He
can send it the way He wants to send it.

00:12:58.206 --> 00:13:10.271
Even to challenge this shows the mental
mind which is in, absolutely in mud.

00:13:14.005 --> 00:13:19.063
So to accept it is only possible

00:13:19.264 --> 00:13:23.221
when you have saints, real saints who
tell you,

00:13:23.422 --> 00:13:29.917
that this is how Shri Ganesha was born
out of Gauri.

00:13:34.206 --> 00:13:38.417
But to jump into it, into faith,

00:13:38.618 --> 00:13:44.741
when you come to Sahaja Yoga, you start
seeing miracles taking place.

00:13:45.791 --> 00:13:50.119
Then you can understand that these miracles
are taking place

00:13:50.320 --> 00:13:56.404
and if there is another miracle that has to
take place it will take place in any case.

00:13:56.605 --> 00:14:01.077
 We are not doing anything, it’s all done.

00:14:02.004 --> 00:14:08.247
And we don't doubt it. Once you doubt
you become again the same

00:14:10.339 --> 00:14:15.736
human being which is just embedded
in the mud.

00:14:17.460 --> 00:14:22.009
I always say that you are like lotuses now
opened out.

00:14:22.210 --> 00:14:25.914
You are not flying in the air. Your roots
are down there.

00:14:26.115 --> 00:14:31.425
But you are now lotuses,

00:14:31.626 --> 00:14:38.836
and that's what is on top of the lotus,
this Mahalakshmi principle is born.

00:14:39.037 --> 00:14:45.543
Mahalakshmi principle is the One which
came on this earth

00:14:45.744 --> 00:14:56.842
as Sitaji, as Radha and also as Mary,
as Mother Mary.

00:14:57.160 --> 00:15:02.997
It's said that Mahalakshmi is born out
of the sea.

00:15:03.198 --> 00:15:09.969
What is the meaning of "Mary"? Maria means,
you know, Marine means "the sea".

00:15:11.714 --> 00:15:14.418
She was born out of the sea.

00:15:14.619 --> 00:15:21.282
So She being a Mahalakshmi Herself, She
could create a child. What's the harm?

00:15:23.845 --> 00:15:27.276
She could do anything,

00:15:29.756 --> 00:15:33.191
and this is the thing you have to rise
above.

00:15:33.392 --> 00:15:37.328
Christians have to rise above this
Christianity,

00:15:37.529 --> 00:15:41.522
and has to understand that it's such
a great thing that was Christ

00:15:41.723 --> 00:15:48.240
Who came on this earth, Who was the
Incarnation of the principle of Ganesha.

00:15:48.441 --> 00:15:51.365
Ganesha becoming Mahavishnu is
a very big thing

00:15:51.566 --> 00:15:54.642
which one should try to understand.

00:15:54.843 --> 00:16:01.719
Ganesha is the Son of Shiva.

00:16:02.576 --> 00:16:14.549
Shri Ganesha is the One Who was first
created before creating anything,

00:16:15.755 --> 00:16:22.610
any atmosphere, anything, because He is
the Omkara,

00:16:22.811 --> 00:16:28.843
and the Omkara is the first breaking
of Adi Shakti from Shiva.

00:16:29.044 --> 00:16:33.952
That sound, "Tan-kar", as they call it.
From there started Omkara

00:16:34.153 --> 00:16:39.205
and He is the One Who is the embodiment
of that Omkara.

00:16:39.406 --> 00:16:43.238
So this sound is Shri Ganesh, is His power,

00:16:43.439 --> 00:16:51.743
was created first foremost thing, just
to create holiness, pavitrata.

00:16:51.944 --> 00:16:56.189
When this holiness was created, this
pavitrata was created,

00:16:56.390 --> 00:17:03.253
then everything was created in the sea
of that holiness.

00:17:04.777 --> 00:17:12.572
And then He incarnated as Christ, but
as Mahavishnu,

00:17:12.773 --> 00:17:18.271
not as Shiva's Son, but as Mahavishnu.

00:17:18.472 --> 00:17:26.191
And who is Vishnu? He is an uncle
of Shri Ganesh.

00:17:27.016 --> 00:17:34.151
His Mother's brother is Shri Vishnu.

00:17:35.286 --> 00:17:41.046
So the, it was brought up, we should say,
by Mahavishnu, we can say,

00:17:41.247 --> 00:17:47.893
but Mahalakshmi adopted the principle
of Shri Ganesh.

00:17:48.094 --> 00:17:51.194
In the Kundalini chart you can see that
the Shri Ganesha

00:17:51.395 --> 00:17:56.300
is connected on the left-hand side
to the Ida Nadi,

00:17:59.821 --> 00:18:03.748
and the Kundalini is above that.

00:18:03.949 --> 00:18:11.013
So now what has happened is this, that
He transcended that part,

00:18:11.214 --> 00:18:13.914
and if He had to come for the redemption,

00:18:14.115 --> 00:18:19.181
He had to come as the Son of Mahalakshmi.

00:18:19.382 --> 00:18:22.766
So it was Mahalakshmi who adopted Him,

00:18:22.967 --> 00:18:30.633
or we should say, really conceived Him
within Himself as Christ,

00:18:33.906 --> 00:18:36.445
and He became Mahavishnu.

00:18:36.646 --> 00:18:45.164
Anything is possible in the family of Gods
and Goddesses, because they are Gods.

00:18:47.177 --> 00:18:52.713
It is beyond human mind to understand
how these things

00:18:52.914 --> 00:18:59.547
are working out in that realm. Very
difficult.

00:19:00.102 --> 00:19:03.790
But now you have got Realization, you can
feel in the cool breeze,

00:19:03.991 --> 00:19:08.363
so many new things are happening to you.
So now believe Me,

00:19:08.564 --> 00:19:13.536
that there is no unholy alliances

00:19:13.737 --> 00:19:16.682
among the Gods and Goddesses, no
unholy alliances.

00:19:16.883 --> 00:19:21.643
There is nothing that is human in them.

00:19:21.844 --> 00:19:28.101
They are all divine, pure people.

00:19:30.212 --> 00:19:33.519
Once you understand this point, then
you will understand

00:19:33.720 --> 00:19:43.858
why Shri Ganesha had to accept to be
a Son of Mahalakshmi,

00:19:44.059 --> 00:19:48.398
was born to Him as Christ.

00:19:48.599 --> 00:19:56.158
Because He had to come on Agnya,
and for the redemption,

00:19:56.359 --> 00:20:01.936
as Ganesha, He doesn't do the redemption
part,

00:20:02.137 --> 00:20:10.401
because at that stage He is for
the innocence, for the holiness,

00:20:10.602 --> 00:20:17.740
for the wisdom or also for destroying
a negativity.

00:20:17.949 --> 00:20:23.722
But He had to come up; only He,

00:20:23.923 --> 00:20:34.109
only Ganesha could be brought to this
very constricted chakra, Agnya chakra.

00:20:34.998 --> 00:20:38.046
Now why is it constricted? It's quite
a scientific thing

00:20:38.247 --> 00:20:40.898
which I would not like to discuss today.

00:20:41.099 --> 00:20:43.571
But it had to be constricted

00:20:43.772 --> 00:20:47.099
and it goes on getting more constricted,
this Agnya chakra,

00:20:47.300 --> 00:20:54.615
the more, the more we think, the more
we go into the left or right,

00:20:54.816 --> 00:20:59.365
it goes on really becoming like this,
absolutely like this.

00:20:59.566 --> 00:21:07.443
So in this very subtle area only Christ
could be settled,

00:21:07.644 --> 00:21:11.782
because He is the subtlest of subtle.

00:21:13.471 --> 00:21:18.351
He's even subtler than an atom, because
in the atom

00:21:18.552 --> 00:21:23.134
those vibrations which move asymmetric
and symmetric movements

00:21:23.335 --> 00:21:28.218
are subtler than the atom.

00:21:28.419 --> 00:21:31.635
And this is the subtler of that also.

00:21:31.836 --> 00:21:36.886
So in that little very constricted area,

00:21:37.087 --> 00:21:46.706
only a personality like Christ, which is
nothing but purity.

00:21:46.907 --> 00:21:59.380
There is no other element in Him
but purity.

00:21:59.928 --> 00:22:08.598
All other Incarnations have all the five
elements in it.

00:22:08.799 --> 00:22:15.396
He has nothing. He is nothing but pure
vibrations.

00:22:15.597 --> 00:22:19.322
That's why He could walk on the water,

00:22:19.523 --> 00:22:27.525
because there was no mass in His body,
no matter in His body. No matter.

00:22:27.726 --> 00:22:33.051
No element, except for Chaitanya itself.

00:22:33.282 --> 00:22:38.643
Omkara becoming Ganesha in the mud,

00:22:38.844 --> 00:22:44.282
or the what you can say, the thing that
came out of Her body.

00:22:44.483 --> 00:22:49.080
Only the Chaitanya. So at Ganesha's stage
we can say

00:22:49.281 --> 00:22:53.971
that the Chaitanya was kept in that form,

00:22:54.172 --> 00:23:00.834
but in the state of Christ it was no
longer there.

00:23:04.082 --> 00:23:09.691
But the whole drama was played later on,
of His death and resurrection,

00:23:09.892 --> 00:23:13.942
because He is the One who is responsible
for our resurrection,

