00:41:04.484 --> 00:41:05.520
But,

00:41:07.007 --> 00:41:09.098
The supreme God is watching,

00:41:11.072 --> 00:41:13.072
how you all are behaving?

00:41:14.960 --> 00:41:20.471
After a lot of hard work, We,
that is your Mother gave you all Sahaja Yoga,

00:41:22.227 --> 00:41:25.161
And where is your foot wobbling?

00:41:26.693 --> 00:41:29.190
What mistake are you doing now?

00:41:30.592 --> 00:41:33.600
And so you should act with understanding.

00:41:35.306 --> 00:41:39.639
But, I would say that, Adishakti is definitely
the power of the God almighty,

00:41:40.583 --> 00:41:42.054
She is His desire.

00:41:42.682 --> 00:41:45.402
But, The God almighty, is watching,

00:41:46.143 --> 00:41:48.610
that all the hard work that is happening,

00:41:48.811 --> 00:41:51.181
and in the drama created by Her,

00:41:51.382 --> 00:41:54.156
how many are truthful and untruthful.

00:41:54.548 --> 00:41:58.238
And He is calculating, who all should be taken to task.

00:41:58.786 --> 00:42:02.046
Whoever is good, also should be
considered sometimes, right?

00:42:02.247 --> 00:42:03.524
It’s not like that.

00:42:04.064 --> 00:42:07.576
But whoever is insincere,
He will catch them.

00:42:08.165 --> 00:42:09.862
And He will give everybody a blow.

00:42:10.073 --> 00:42:11.673
That is why, kindly,

00:42:12.136 --> 00:42:14.303
do whatever you have to,

00:42:14.695 --> 00:42:18.279
with a clean heart,
with a open heart.

00:42:18.486 --> 00:42:21.587
I have not told you before that if you have other interests within,

00:42:21.788 --> 00:42:24.849
if you have blind faith, if you have casteism within you,

00:42:25.050 --> 00:42:28.447
Or if you have “we Indians are great” kind of feeling within you,

00:42:28.648 --> 00:42:31.403
These kind of feelings are myth, it has no purity,

00:42:31.652 --> 00:42:35.461
You kindly get rid of all these feelings, and then wear my pendent.

00:42:35.662 --> 00:42:39.084
Because with each pendent one “Gana” is appointed.

00:42:40.280 --> 00:42:42.382
And they (ganas) are around you.

00:42:42.668 --> 00:42:44.496
They always protect you,

00:42:44.697 --> 00:42:49.199
in a way they protect you to stop you from doing wrong things.

00:42:53.557 --> 00:42:56.217
Because, they know you in and out.

00:42:56.988 --> 00:43:02.335
So, today this warning also was very essential for you all.

00:43:03.426 --> 00:43:06.080
And also, it is a very happy occasion

00:43:06.358 --> 00:43:11.993
that if, In this world, Jesus Christ had not come,

00:43:12.588 --> 00:43:16.101
and if he had not made us sit on his Agnya Chakra,

00:43:16.727 --> 00:43:20.133
and opened the path of rebirth,

00:43:20.600 --> 00:43:25.052
path of resurrection, then Sahaja Yoga wouldn’t have been possible.

00:43:25.352 --> 00:43:27.460
 It was very essential that He took birth.

00:43:27.661 --> 00:43:30.781
But there is no fight among themselves.
All of them (incarnations) are,

00:43:30.982 --> 00:43:33.310
born on one single tree,

00:43:33.511 --> 00:43:36.286
on a living tree they all were created

00:43:36.487 --> 00:43:39.384
and this tree was flourished finally I came on Sahasrara,

00:43:39.585 --> 00:43:42.960
and this work (Sahaja Yoga) happened in Sahasrara.

00:43:44.547 --> 00:43:47.468
If tree is not there, how can Sahasrara be there?

00:43:48.206 --> 00:43:52.508
And if the Sahasrara is there, then this tree only has created that Sahasrara.

00:43:52.709 --> 00:43:57.394
 So, it is the responsibility of the tree also to take care of the Sahasrara,

00:43:58.354 --> 00:44:03.575
and protect it completely, and punish those who go against it (Sahasrara).

00:44:07.018 --> 00:44:10.800
So, for all of you, today is in a very special sense,

00:44:11.205 --> 00:44:14.613
is of importance, that if Jesus Christ had not come,

00:44:14.814 --> 00:44:17.750
then, our resurrection wouldn’t have happened.

00:44:17.951 --> 00:44:22.782
Because, we tell Shri Ganesha that when our time for moksha comes,

00:44:22.983 --> 00:44:24.760
you please protect us.

00:44:25.193 --> 00:44:26.463
(inaudible)

00:44:27.964 --> 00:44:32.873
At the time of moksha He Himself (Ganesh) appears,

00:44:33.080 --> 00:44:36.481
on the agnya chakra and gives you protection.

00:44:38.981 --> 00:44:42.840
So Today’s day is very auspicious for all of us,

00:44:43.237 --> 00:44:46.440
very joy giving day also,

00:44:46.655 --> 00:44:50.573
and at the same time cautions us also, that “Be careful”.

00:44:51.017 --> 00:44:53.789
And if you get stuck in “agnya chakra”,

00:44:54.218 --> 00:44:56.823
then you will end up either in a mental asylum,

00:45:00.742 --> 00:45:03.038
or you will get some other disease.

00:45:03.239 --> 00:45:07.896
The sanctity of agnya chakra should be maintained, meaning our thoughts should be pure.

00:45:08.097 --> 00:45:12.555
If impure thoughts come, then we should keep forgiving them.

00:45:13.073 --> 00:45:14.998
Thoughts should always be pure.

00:45:15.199 --> 00:45:19.359
And as you start ascending, you will not get impure thoughts,

00:45:19.560 --> 00:45:21.560
only pure thoughts will come.

00:45:22.255 --> 00:45:27.360
This Sahaja Yoga is made only for your joy,

00:45:27.701 --> 00:45:30.495
for your greatness,

00:45:30.696 --> 00:45:32.391
for your dignity,

00:45:32.645 --> 00:45:36.577
and for your over all progress.

00:45:37.323 --> 00:45:41.721
But along with that this fact also is contained,

00:45:44.255 --> 00:45:46.704
that for this great work,

00:45:47.260 --> 00:45:51.518
and for the people who are completely attached with this work,

00:45:51.915 --> 00:45:56.663
if one does not co-operate and provide their full support,

00:45:57.172 --> 00:45:59.929
also may land up into deep trouble.

00:46:01.282 --> 00:46:04.006
Those who are doing this work wholeheartedly,

00:46:04.207 --> 00:46:07.262
you should support them wholeheartedly.

00:46:07.463 --> 00:46:11.129
In many people now I am noticing the disease of miserliness.

00:46:11.330 --> 00:46:12.513
For example,

00:46:13.974 --> 00:46:19.097
“if 4 rupees can be saved, it is okay, let me save it”.

00:46:20.090 --> 00:46:24.263
If you try to save 4 rupees, you will lose at least 400 rupees,

00:46:24.464 --> 00:46:25.718
just like that.

00:46:27.713 --> 00:46:31.576
And your 1 rupee given to Sahaja Yoga, can be equal to 1 lac rupees.

00:46:31.777 --> 00:46:34.918
Meaning, one rupee will be enough, that’s what I am telling you.

00:46:35.347 --> 00:46:38.247
But we are not giving anything, everything belongs to Mother,

00:46:38.448 --> 00:46:40.159
we are giving Mother, what is Hers.

00:46:40.363 --> 00:46:43.453
And, I don’t take anything, you know that I am trying to resist every day

00:46:43.654 --> 00:46:45.128
 that don’t give me presents,

00:46:45.329 --> 00:46:47.750
I don’t want anything, don’t give Me sarees,

00:46:47.951 --> 00:46:50.622
From morning to evening, since 5 years the tussle is going on,

00:46:50.823 --> 00:46:53.852
no one listens, I have been asking them to reduce buying gifts,

00:46:54.053 --> 00:46:57.606
Now the prices also are increasing, and I don’t need anything.

00:46:58.096 --> 00:47:01.246
But for Sahaja Yoga money is required.

00:47:01.928 --> 00:47:06.818
But there are people here, who feel that eat food for free is right.

00:47:10.159 --> 00:47:14.285
Later if they have stomach problem, I am not responsible for that.

00:47:19.027 --> 00:47:21.960
And this place is not for beggars.

00:47:22.547 --> 00:47:25.660
This is for people who are wealthy by demeanor.

00:47:25.954 --> 00:47:28.201
If you have the mentality of a king, then come here.

00:47:28.402 --> 00:47:30.799
There is no need that you should have money.

00:47:31.000 --> 00:47:33.466
Many rich people are extremely stingy,

00:47:33.667 --> 00:47:36.678
and so peculiar that it is difficult to understand them,

00:47:36.879 --> 00:47:39.095
And many poor people are like Me,

00:47:39.296 --> 00:47:42.454
that they find joy in just giving to others.

00:47:42.820 --> 00:47:45.836
When your one hand opens you take from it.

00:47:46.037 --> 00:47:48.570
But only when the other hand opens, you will get from that hand,

00:47:48.771 --> 00:47:50.636
otherwise it will stop there.

00:47:51.745 --> 00:47:56.166
But when I hear about miserliness, I feel very disgusted you cannot imagine.

00:47:58.675 --> 00:48:02.742
But, I liked the other day’s scene, when there was nothing to give,

00:48:02.943 --> 00:48:05.550
people accepted my photo with affection.

00:48:05.751 --> 00:48:09.440
“Mother, please give us your photo this time, we will feel good”.

00:48:09.726 --> 00:48:11.040
Satisfaction,

00:48:13.088 --> 00:48:14.606
should come first.

00:48:14.820 --> 00:48:19.680
After the satisfaction human being, nobody can sacrifice like Jesus Christ, right?

00:48:20.046 --> 00:48:23.760
But, that sacrifice should be gladly accepted.

00:48:24.141 --> 00:48:26.771
It can be difficult, but it doesn’t matter.

00:48:27.160 --> 00:48:29.327
But we all doing a very great job.

00:48:29.528 --> 00:48:32.920
And not just for us, we are doing it for all others.

00:48:35.825 --> 00:48:37.746
Next year I am going to get your name list.

00:48:37.947 --> 00:48:41.006
and I want to see, specially, about the complain on Bombay people,

00:48:41.207 --> 00:48:44.320
that, they completely refuse to pay money.

00:48:44.890 --> 00:48:48.050
And the Mahalakshmi temple is in this Bombay.

00:48:48.760 --> 00:48:51.586
What is the use of that poor Mahalakshmi and the temple?

00:48:51.787 --> 00:48:54.355
Where Mahalakshmi Herself came out of the earth,

00:48:54.556 --> 00:48:59.345
and in such a place people are so stingy that, they do not want to pay at all,

00:48:59.647 --> 00:49:04.508
thinking that Mother is doing everything, so come, let us just relax and enjoy.

00:49:05.452 --> 00:49:08.480
As such everything will happen whether they pay or not,

00:49:08.774 --> 00:49:11.303
But what will happen to them,

00:49:11.835 --> 00:49:13.200
think of that.

00:49:16.200 --> 00:49:21.349
The quality of Mahalakshmi principle is that, when we become a contented personality,

00:49:21.550 --> 00:49:25.819
when the Lakshmi principle attains maturity, the Mahalakshmi principle gets awakened,

00:49:26.020 --> 00:49:28.362
and we start searching the truth.

00:49:30.024 --> 00:49:32.320
If there is no contentment within you,

00:49:32.995 --> 00:49:35.560
you cannot attain the Mahalakshmi principle

00:49:37.774 --> 00:49:42.158
Look at Seeta Ji’s life, how long did she stay with Ramchandra Ji?

00:49:42.355 --> 00:49:43.837
Radha Ji’s life,

00:49:44.037 --> 00:49:47.896
And after that Shri Jesus Christ’s Mother’s life?

00:49:48.367 --> 00:49:52.280
In all the three lives there is plenty of sacrifice.

00:49:52.534 --> 00:49:55.764
In all the three lives there is plenty of sacrifice.

00:49:55.971 --> 00:49:59.236
So with the Mahalakshmi principle human becomes contented,

00:49:59.477 --> 00:50:00.477
and

00:50:01.778 --> 00:50:05.377
with this principle he seeks the truth,

00:50:06.005 --> 00:50:09.600
And during this seeking, he leaves behind the untruth.

00:50:10.513 --> 00:50:13.382
In today’s Mahalakshmi Puja,

00:50:13.583 --> 00:50:18.904
Where in we are worshipping Jesus Christ, and His mother Mary

00:50:19.150 --> 00:50:22.000
then we should get into total contentment.

00:50:24.939 --> 00:50:29.800
When we get satisfied with materialistic things and worldly things,

00:50:30.475 --> 00:50:34.046
only then the Mahalakshmi principle awakens within us.

00:50:34.960 --> 00:50:40.440
And then, the Mahalakshmi Principle manages the Lakshmi principle.

00:50:41.774 --> 00:50:45.400
And Lakshmi Principle starts manifesting by itself,

00:50:45.860 --> 00:50:50.080
gets implemented by itself and gives the benefit automatically.

00:50:50.397 --> 00:50:53.680
Automatically everything constructive happens.

00:51:02.416 --> 00:51:06.368
So, I just have to tell you that expand your heart.

00:51:07.075 --> 00:51:08.440
Be generous.

00:51:08.702 --> 00:51:11.960
And establish that Omkara within your heart,

00:51:12.254 --> 00:51:16.470
establish that essence of the spirit, establish that Jesus Christ and the Ganesha within you,

00:51:16.772 --> 00:51:18.397
because of whom,

00:51:22.016 --> 00:51:24.551
all our undone work will be done,

00:51:25.036 --> 00:51:27.560
and you can have authority over me.

00:51:28.139 --> 00:51:32.535
Without them I can not give you any right.

00:51:33.822 --> 00:51:38.800
In the raising of Kundalini also, until, from the mooladhar

00:51:41.435 --> 00:51:48.096
 the permission doesn’t come, unless the Ganesha, present in mooladhar says: ” Yes”,

00:51:49.128 --> 00:51:52.526
 not only Me, but no one can raise the Kundalini.

00:51:53.994 --> 00:51:56.760
These are His reserved rights.

00:51:58.355 --> 00:52:01.269
If anybody thinks that He is very close to mother,

00:52:01.470 --> 00:52:04.493
then they should understand that even if He is close,

00:52:04.694 --> 00:52:11.191
and in real He is close to mother then that is happening with Shri Ganesha’s consent,

00:52:11.477 --> 00:52:13.397
Jesus Christ’s consent.

00:52:14.668 --> 00:52:18.280
Without their consent, I can not accept anyone.

00:52:18.610 --> 00:52:20.610
This is a bondage upon us,

00:52:21.166 --> 00:52:25.200
that’s why I tell you again and again that “be careful”.

00:52:25.898 --> 00:52:28.200
Their bondage has to be accepted.

00:52:28.462 --> 00:52:33.840
And whatever is their opinion about you,

00:52:34.237 --> 00:52:36.440
whatever they think about you,

00:52:36.702 --> 00:52:39.040
I have to take into consideration.

00:52:39.484 --> 00:52:43.501
How ever hard I may forgive, from a mother’s point of view whatever I may say,

00:52:43.702 --> 00:52:45.867
But I am lost in front of these deities (Jesus and Ganesha).

00:52:46.068 --> 00:52:51.880
And You should know that, “They” are there to help you, to cleanse you,

00:52:52.237 --> 00:52:54.013
and do everything for you,

00:52:54.214 --> 00:52:57.942
But “They” have one expectation from you, I have no expectations, I am without expectations,

00:52:58.143 --> 00:53:01.351
I don’t want anything from you, however you are it is fine.

00:53:01.552 --> 00:53:07.522
But, “They” have expectations that, if you say or do anything against Me,

00:53:08.035 --> 00:53:11.282
or if you do any kind of “pettiness” in Sahaja Yoga,

00:53:11.483 --> 00:53:15.999
or you do any kind of cheating or any such thing, then “They” will be behind you.

00:53:16.200 --> 00:53:18.294
  That’s why I am telling you again and again, on this day,

00:53:18.495 --> 00:53:20.774
on this auspicious occasion, we should realize,

00:53:20.975 --> 00:53:24.037
 that, such great powers are standing by our side.

00:53:24.238 --> 00:53:28.640
And why shouldn’t we accept these powers and live like an emperor?

00:53:28.870 --> 00:53:32.687
And why should we be “Petty minded”, when we have such a big throne,

00:53:32.888 --> 00:53:35.179
then let us sit on the throne with dignity.

00:53:35.380 --> 00:53:38.486
And let us live with that dignity, as we are supposed to.

00:53:38.687 --> 00:53:41.437
Now you all are Sahaja Yogis, you are saints,

00:53:41.638 --> 00:53:44.206
it is a very great thing, when were there so many Yogis?

00:53:44.407 --> 00:53:47.800
And so many saints have come to “Ganapatipule”,

00:53:48.086 --> 00:53:51.294
where in Maha Ganesha is sitting, He is called Maha Ganesha.

00:53:51.495 --> 00:53:53.198
And in the Maha Ganesha’s

00:53:57.104 --> 00:53:59.143
family, we all have joined.

00:53:59.493 --> 00:54:01.960
We have come to His forum.

00:54:02.310 --> 00:54:08.462
And with His blessings, within us also, great powers as He has, can manifest.

00:54:08.663 --> 00:54:13.400
But first of all, to withstand that power, His purity should be established.

00:54:14.059 --> 00:54:16.541
and there should be a devotion (bhakti) towards him.

00:54:16.742 --> 00:54:22.441
The bhakti should be in such a way that, there is no selfishness of any kind in that.

00:54:22.688 --> 00:54:24.275
There is only Bhakti.

00:54:24.553 --> 00:54:28.202
If we can ready ourselves like Him, then He takes care of rest of the things.

00:54:28.403 --> 00:54:30.590
Then He is at your disposal to manage you.

00:54:30.791 --> 00:54:35.920
But if you go on the opposite side, He may also harm you.

00:54:36.587 --> 00:54:38.031
just like that,

00:54:40.440 --> 00:54:43.070
I want to make you understand something sensible.

00:54:43.271 --> 00:54:49.760
Because a mother always feels that, these children of mine are very sweet,

00:54:50.196 --> 00:54:53.360
and you should only benefit from them (deities).

00:54:53.884 --> 00:54:58.240
Then I also feel that you should not feel sorry later.

00:54:58.653 --> 00:55:01.800
 That is why, I am explaining to you,

00:55:02.157 --> 00:55:05.099
when we have created such beautiful atmosphere here,

00:55:05.300 --> 00:55:09.566
and gathered like one family members,

00:55:09.844 --> 00:55:11.477
and we all are together,

00:55:11.678 --> 00:55:17.440
then these elder brothers of yours should be acknowledged by you,

00:55:17.988 --> 00:55:21.520
that they are present and they should be recognized.

00:55:21.774 --> 00:55:26.217
And if you worship them and make them happy, it will be really good.

00:55:26.487 --> 00:55:28.881
But they don’t get pleased so soon.

00:55:29.318 --> 00:55:32.806
Until you are cleansed from within, they won’t be happy.

00:55:33.007 --> 00:55:36.761
So you clean yourself from within, and take a vow today

00:55:36.962 --> 00:55:41.009
that, in future we will completely discard all types of pettiness,

00:55:41.210 --> 00:55:44.719
frivolous act, and trivial matters.

00:55:45.228 --> 00:55:48.806
And we shall look up to these deities’ greatness and purity

00:55:49.007 --> 00:55:52.399
and consider them as our ideals and steer our lives in that direction.

00:55:52.600 --> 00:55:56.400
If we do just this, it will be our benefit from all sides.

00:55:56.924 --> 00:55:58.892
My infinite blessings to you.

00:55:59.208 --> 00:56:03.096
And you all have come here with lots of love,

00:56:06.224 --> 00:56:09.040
I can not say thanks to you all,

00:56:10.072 --> 00:56:12.565
but it is just that my heart is deeply moved.

00:56:12.766 --> 00:56:15.425
and in this heart, you all are residing,

00:56:15.775 --> 00:56:18.192
and I love you all too much.

00:56:18.407 --> 00:56:22.080
and I look at you with immeasurable love.

00:56:22.342 --> 00:56:25.902
and my thoughts are always around your protection.

00:56:26.103 --> 00:56:29.800
My total attention and thoughts are towards you

00:56:30.268 --> 00:56:35.048
and for any kind of problem you can write to me,

00:56:35.278 --> 00:56:37.774
but you yourself should become pure,

00:56:37.975 --> 00:56:40.240
you should become clean,

00:56:40.454 --> 00:56:46.400
and you should become delightful and experience this joy till eternity.
